    • Method Detail

      • getEnumByPropertyValueIgnoreCase

        public static <E extends Enum<?>,T> E getEnumByPropertyValueIgnoreCase(Class<E> enumClass,
                                                                       String propertyName,
                                                                       T specifiedValue)
        通过propertyName的 value(忽视大小写) 获得枚举(equalsIgnoreCase判断). 
         
 适用于这种HttpMethodType 待自定义属性的枚举类型,调用方式:
 
 
  EnumUtil.getEnumByField(HttpMethodType.class, "method", "get")
        Type Parameters:
        E - the element type
        T - the generic type
        Parameters:
        enumClass - the enum class 比如 HttpMethodType
        propertyName - 字段名称,比如 HttpMethodType的method,按照javabean 规范
        specifiedValue - 属性值 比如post
        Returns:
        获得 enum constant
        See Also:
        getEnumByPropertyValue(Class, String, Object, boolean)
